This is a mirror of http://www.vim.org/scripts/script.php?script_id=5056

A very fast fork of vimscript #2150 with extra features:

 multiple color highlights per line
 rgb(), rgba(), hsl() support for CSS
 support for various alternative CSS languages like Less and Sass
 support for various non-CSS languages like VimL and Lua

Screenshot available at
https://github.com/ap/vim-css-color
